 Now, he was not a Christian, but we were talking about faith

10
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:29,560
 and this was almost weekly.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:32,200
 And he asked a lot of like challenging questions.

12
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,160
 This was, were not easy conversations,

13
